ai-patthana17.23:0.2_0: (This should be expanded as in the teachings.)
ai-patthana17.23:0.3_0: should apply themselves to the skillful.
ai-patthana17.23:1.1_0: Neither comes up with grasping, but not because of grasping. ...
ai-patthana17.23:2.1_0: Neither grasp at ease, but not because of grasping. ...
ai-patthana17.23:3.1_0: Pūraṇa Kassapa doesn’t give rise to the unskillful. There’s no cause or condition for the reason.
ai-patthana17.23:4.1_0: An unprotected principle, not with grasping.
